'''Allmovie'''（原名'''All Movie Guide'''）是一個包含關於[[電影明星|電影明星]]、[[電影|電影]]與[[電視劇|電視劇]]資訊的商業資料庫<ref name="isbn1-55652-550-8">{{cite book |author=Michael Haddad |authorlink= |editor= |others= |title=The screenwriter's sourcebook: a comprehensive marketing guide for screen and television writers |edition= |language= |publisher=Chicago Review Press |location=Chicago, Ill |year=2005 |origyear= |quote= |isbn=1-55652-550-8 |oclc= |doi= |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6FXysyLEdoQC&pg=PA333&dq=Allmovie&lr=lang_en&num=20&as_brr=3&ei=krZySLXCKaCmigGJ1vGABg&sig=ACfU3U1iMXjt3Bj9IYN6-k7ZzGSSVhekUA |accessdate= |page=333 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528053609/http://books.google.com/books?id=6FXysyLEdoQC&pg=PA333&dq=Allmovie&lr=lang_en&num=20&as_brr=3&ei=krZySLXCKaCmigGJ1vGABg&sig=ACfU3U1iMXjt3Bj9IYN6-k7ZzGSSVhekUA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="isbn1-59337-334-1">{{cite book |author=Malone, Michael |authorlink= |editor= |others= |title=The Everything College Survival Book: From Social Life To Study Skills--all You Need To Fit Right In (Everything: School and Careers) |edition= |language= |publisher=Adams Media Corporation |location=Avon, MA |year=2005 |origyear= |quote= |isbn=1-59337-334-1 |oclc= |doi= |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IlEtGM7dlNkC&pg=PT294&dq=Allmovie&lr=lang_en&num=20&as_brr=3&ei=krZySLXCKaCmigGJ1vGABg&sig=ACfU3U0xVj7a25d9Kas0WszA_q6PSA0gcg |accessdate= |page=281 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528045438/http://books.google.com/books?id=IlEtGM7dlNkC&pg=PT294&dq=Allmovie&lr=lang_en&num=20&as_brr=3&ei=krZySLXCKaCmigGJ1vGABg&sig=ACfU3U0xVj7a25d9Kas0WszA_q6PSA0gcg |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它由電影資料庫維護者Michael Erlewine與擁有數學[[哲學博士|哲學博士]]學位的Vladimir Bogdanov共同創辦，兩人亦創辦了[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]與[[Allgame|Allgame]]。

==历史==
該資料庫已授權給成千上萬個發行商與[[銷售時點情報系統|銷售時點情報系統]]、網站與報攤使用。Allmovie資料庫非常豐富與廣泛，當中包含了基本的產品資訊、演員與製作人員名單、情節概要、傳記、專家評論與相關鏈接等。

Allmovie上的資料可透過網路於allmovie.com網站存取，亦可經由可自動識別DVD的媒體識別服務[[AMG_LASSO|AMG LASSO]]存取。

該網站是[[All_Media_Guide|All Media Guide]]的產品，其他還有[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]與[[Allgame|Allgame]]。

2011年，Allmovie与Allmusic被整合至[[Rovi公司|Rovi公司]]创办的'''Allrovi'''。

